name: FixedOrderComparator_compareTest
description: Unit tests for the compare method of FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareKnownObjects
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison of known objects in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectBefore
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison of unknown objects with behavior set to BEFORE in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectAfter
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison of unknown objects with behavior set to AFTER in the FixedOrderComparator.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectException
test_cases.description: Tests the comparison of unknown objects with behavior set to EXCEPTION in the FixedOrderComparator, expecting an IllegalArgumentException.

test_cases.name: testCompareUnknownObjectBehaviorNull
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of setting null as the unknown object behavior in the FixedOrderComparator, expecting a NullPointerException.

test_cases.name: testCompareAfterLock
test_cases.description: Tests the behavior of adding an object after the comparator has been locked, expecting an UnsupportedOperationException.
